node.text:
Back when @forsure__nodoubt was in town last year we were lucky enough to catch a Session with him and his filmer @rudygarciaphoto at one of our local parks Rowley. We originally planned on filming Reece but Rudy was also skating around so we got a few clips of him as well. Rudy films all kinds of scooter videos so it's nice too see him in one for a change 😉

@ethicdtc @riverwheelco @endsfootwear

video by @jameswebby

#tvps #goride #ripDOOM

node.title: Vault Sessions - Reece Doezema and Rudy Garcia

node.text:
We present to you @walt3rperez Session from Mayberry Skatepark in Whittier! We headed 
 out one day in hopes of having a session before work and man did it pay off. We actually even got kicked out as the park was still closed at the time. Still had a great time and we managed to put this video together, enjoy!

Let us know if you guys want to see more from Walter!

As seen in Vault Rides Episode 7 on our Youtube

video by @jameswebby

#tvps

node.title: Vault Sessions - Walter Perez at Mayberry Skatepark

node.text:
Taking it back to better times; Just as the pandemic hit we were working on Vault Rides 6 and trying to get as much riding content as possible. The final part we filmed was @thegrapeslushies 

One nice afternoon one we headed out to Rosemead and had a wonderful Session. Sean was on one that day and we easily got 4 minutes of footage! Enjoy this edit newly uploaded to IGTV!

More riding content soon!

video by @jameswebby

#tvps #goride

node.text:
We're back with another Vault Session and this time we have our boys @austinspencerr and @walt3rperez We woke up extremely early one day to hit Denny's, film this video, and then be at work by 11. It ended up going pretty well as we were able to put a 5 minute video together. Anyway enjoy watching the boys get after it. 
More from Vault Rides 6 on our YouTube and soon on IGTV!

#TVPS #STAYSAFE

video by @jameswebby

node.text: During Quarantine here in California, Rocco Piazza (@roccopiazza) stopped by to cop a rail and we couldnt pass up the opportunity to film a Custom Build with him. The ony problem is none of our filmers we’re here so Austin Spencer (@austinspencerr) stepped in with little to no filming experience. Don’t worry tho guys, as soon as quarantine ends we'll be back to our normal upload schedule! #tvps

Welcome to the team @delaneyball24! 🤝🛴

node.text:
If you guys weren’t able to be at the Seattle Street Jam this last weekend, here’s a recap of @caaaalub destroying the spots 🦑 I’m sure a lot of you saw the guys and girls killing it, but we’re throwing the spotlight on Caleb today #tvps 

If you’re a young up and coming rider, stay dedicated and get your basic tricks down! One of the fastest ways to progressing is learning every basic trick there is and being able to throw it down at any spot. Invest in yourself now, so that it pays off later 💰

node.text:
Left or right? 👈👉 let us know! 

Last week we got a big shipment of @aztek so we’re throwing up 2/4 colors of their scs and fork! You can’t beat that signature red color in the bolts 💯 #tvps

node.text: Vault Team rider @liamfellows_ was in town last week, and stopped by to film a Custom Build! He decided to replicate his own personal setup, and if you guys want to see more. Make sure to check out the full video over on our YouTube channel. #tvps
